# Keep directory structure but ignore personal content.
# Template/placeholder files (profile.md stubs) are tracked;
# everything appended at runtime is not.

# Measurements, health, milestones logs — runtime-appended
kids/*/measurements.md
kids/*/health.md
kids/*/milestones.md

# Reminders inbox — runtime-appended
reminders/inbox.md

# Weekly sync notes — generated at runtime
syncs/

# Household notes — may contain personal info
household/notes.md

# People contacts — personal info
people/contacts.md
